    "red_box_msg": "The array-sorting metrics and heuristic evaluation speeds outlined here reflect an unmodified application state. Third-party APKs disrupt the secure pattern-validation handshake, leading to localized logic desynchronization. Always source the application from official developer nodes to ensure structural integrity and prevent memory corruption.",
    "yellow_box_msg": "To maintain the optimal UI memory indexing times detailed in this audit, we recommend periodically flushing your device's background RAM during extended simulation sessions. The drag-and-drop physics engine requires unfragmented memory allocation to process heuristic validations without inducing micro-stutters.",
