    "yellow_box_msg": "To replicate the seamless state-machine fluidity measured in our diagnostic, verify that your device is not bottlenecked by fragmented background memory. The engine relies on strict cache-coherency; manually clearing your OS RAM prior to a session allows the localized application to process event-driven inputs with zero micro-stuttering",
