    "release_notes": "Pipeline Bottleneck Resolution (Bug Fixes): Addressed localized desynchronization within the background instruction pipeline. The client-side architecture now efficiently flushes orphaned memory calls, eliminating localized freeze-frames and micro-stutters during rapid physical input sequences.\nAdvanced Hitbox Raycasting (New Features): Deployed a highly optimized coordinate-detection algorithm. The engine now utilizes precise hitbox raycasting to calculate intersection points on multi-layered UI assets, drastically lowering touch-latency and improving drag-and-drop registration accuracy.",
