    "release_notes": "Logic Desynchronization Resolution (Bug Fixes): Addressed floating-point calculation discrepancies between the client-side engine and backend validation nodes. The architecture now ensures absolute deterministic execution, eliminating localized state-sync errors during complex multi-variable tactical scenarios.\nDynamic Asset Streaming (New Features): Deployed a highly optimized background memory protocol. The localized system now streams UI assets dynamically into the active RAM buffer, drastically reducing initial application load times and preventing memory bottlenecking during rapid screen transitions.",
